com.example.n8tech.taskcan.Models

Class BiddedTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.n8tech.taskcan.Models.BiddedTask

  • public class BiddedTask
extends java.lang.Object
    BiddedTask represents a task bidded on by the current user. This encapsulates fields and methods related to tasks the user has bidded on.
    Author:
    CMPUT301W18T06
    See Also:
    Task, Bid

        Creates a BiddedTask object with the minimum details as specified by requirements.
        Parameters:
        name - name of the task with a maximum length of 30 characters
        description - brief description of the task with a maximum length of 300 characters
        ownerUsername - username of the task requester
        ownerId - task requester ID
        category - category the task belongs to
